RelatedSentence: ( KMTV ) - The Omaha Police Department 's Homicide Unit issued a warrant for the arrest of Anthony Burries , for first degree murder .
Police arrested Burries Monday night in Odessa , Missouri .
Police went to Tina Hoult 's apartment near 98th and Mockingbird early Sunday  morning for a welfare check .
Police have not said how Hoult died , or if she knew Burries .
